Package: OptionSuite
Title: Comprehensive Option Pricing and Analysis Suite: Core Foundation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fabio", "Spreafico", , "spreafab@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the core foundation for option pricing and analysis.
    Includes S3 classes for options and underlyings, European option pricing
    via RQuantLib (Black-Scholes), American option pricing via the
    Bjerksund-Stensland 2002 closed-form approximation, and full Greeks
    (delta, gamma, vega, theta, rho). Features flexible expiry input
    (Date, character, numeric), three construction modes (price only,
    volatility only, or both), and global settings for risk-free rate
    and day-count convention.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
